<br><br><p><b><font size="4"><b><font color="Dark Red">IBERIA PARISH PRESIDENT M LARRY RICHARD - (IBERIA COPE) COVID-19 OPERATIONAL PROCEDURES FOR EMPLOYERS</font></b></font></b><font size="3"> -  6/19/2020</font><br><font size="2">Emergency</font></p>
		<p><font size="2">For more information contact: <a href="mailto:pmarshall@iberiagov.net">Prescott Marshall</a>
		<p>Iberia Parish will continue its compliance with the Governor’s Proclamation No. 2020 JBE 41 which can be found at (Link to Stay At Home Document) . As such, we remain under a statewide order in which we have been directed to stay at home unless performing one of the essential activities described in Section 2A of the Governor’s Proclamation.  Furthermore, all gatherings of ten (10) people or more have been ordered postponed or cancelled. </p>
